<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main>
  <section class="page-hero">
    <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>What are your opening times?</h3>
      <p>WildRoots Adventure Park is open every day from 9am to 6pm, 365 days a year.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>How many habitats are there?</h3>
      <p>There are three habitats — Rainforest Canopy, Savannah Plains and Reptile World.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Is the park suitable for young children?</h3>
      <p>Absolutely! WildRoots is a family friendly park with activities and exhibits suited to all ages.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Is there food available at the park?</h3>
      <p>Yes, we have several cafes and restaurants located throughout the park serving hot and cold food all day.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Is the park accessible for wheelchair users?</h3>
      <p>Yes, the majority of the park is fully accessible. Please contact us for specific accessibility information.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can I bring my own food?</h3>
      <p>Yes, picnics are welcome in our designated picnic areas throughout the park.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Are dogs allowed?</h3>
      <p>We love dogs but for the safety of our animals only registered assistance dogs are permitted inside the park.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Is there parking available?</h3>
      <p>Yes, we have a large free car park on site with spaces for cars, coaches and vehicles with disability badges.</p>
    </div>

  </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>